---

<section id="now" class="section now">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="now__inner">
      <div class="now__header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">Right now</p>
        <h2>A living snapshot</h2>
        <p class="now__meta">Last updated: March 2026</p>
      </div>
      <div class="now__grid">
        <div class="now__col reveal reveal-delay-1">
          <h3 class="now__col-title">At work</h3>
          <ul class="now__list">
            <li>Software Engineer — Lead, building medical administration software for a healthcare department.</li>
            <li>Newly in the lead role, figuring out what good leadership looks like from the inside of it rather than the textbook version.</li>
            <li>Focused on clarity: better definitions of done, lighter processes, more reliable releases.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now__col reveal reveal-delay-2">
          <h3 class="now__col-title">Building</h3>
          <ul class="now__list">
            <li>A foodie app for the places algorithms never surface: neighbourhood finds, unsung spots, the ones worth knowing.</li>
            <li>A community collaboration platform for gated communities and neighbourhoods.</li>
            <li>Both in early development with long-time collaborators. Launching regardless.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="now__col reveal reveal-delay-3">
          <h3 class="now__col-title">Learning & exploring</h3>
          <ul class="now__list">
            <li>Electronics fundamentals, working toward DIY security and physical computing projects.</li>
            <li>Thinking seriously about game development as a creative direction with friends.</li>
            <li>Considering structured study: a BA or IT leadership programme from 2026.</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .now {
    background: var(--surface);
    border-block: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .now__inner {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .now__header h2 {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .now__meta {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-dim);
  }

  .now__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .now__col {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .now__col-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--accent);
    letter-spacing: 0.01em;
  }

  .now__list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.85rem;
  }

  .now__list li {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .now__list li::before {
    content: "—";
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--text-dim);
    font-size: 0.75em;
    top: 0.3em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .now__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
